      { type:"fill", q:"A rifle that has been 'bedded' has had its action and/or barrel fitted with a precision interface to the stock, improving ___.", options:["Magazine capacity","Accuracy and consistency","Recoil reduction only","Barrel cooling"], correct:1, explanation:"Bedding (glass or pillar bedding) creates a perfect, rigid fit between action and stock, eliminating inconsistent pressure that degrades accuracy." }
